New in version 0.8.2
---------------------
This version is a through redesign of the package and should be seen 
as a new package altogether.

Current capabilities include:
o Inputs RDS file formats.
o Optimization using coordinate-wise root finding. Fast and stable.
o beta_k are estimated seperatly for each k.
o Coefficient of discoverability can be recovered from beta_k estimates.
o Continous time recruitment simulator.
o Curitiba drug users data set included.




